flowchart TD
    Start([User Access Application]) --> A{Choose Action}
    A --> B[Submit Request]
    A --> C[Admin Panel]

    B --> D[Fill Request Form]
    D --> E{Validate Input}
    E -->|Invalid| F[Show Error Message]
    F --> D
    E -->|Valid| G[Save to Database]
    G --> H[Show Success Message]
    H --> I[Redirect to Form]

    C --> J[View All Requests]
    J --> K{Select Action}
    K --> L[Update Status]
    K --> M[View Details]

    L --> N[Select New Status]
    N --> O[Update Database]
    O --> P[Show Confirmation]
    P --> J

    M --> Q[Display Request Details]
    Q --> J

    style Start fill:#e3f2fd
